OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start to Easter
OL,6,FMonday but the cloud will break up
OL,7,Fthroughout the morning, to give a
OL,8,Fsunny afternoon for many. Lighter
OL,9,Fwinds will allow it to feel a little
OL,10,Fwarmer.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA dry and clear night to come
OL,13,Fwith perhaps a few mist and fog
OL,14,Fpatches forming. A chilly night with
OL,15,Fperhaps a touch of frost in the
OL,16,Fcountryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
