OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA dry and fine day on Tuesday
OL,6,Fwith plenty of sunshine, although
OL,7,Fskies may turn hazy across western
OL,8,Fareas by the afternoon. Feeling warm,
OL,9,Fespecially in the sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FLargely dry with warm spells of
OL,13,Fsunshine on Wednesday. Turning cooler
OL,14,Fand more changeable from Thursday with
OL,15,Fspells of rain and showers moving
OL,16,Facross the region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
